Package nzilbb.labbcat.server.db

Graph Store implementations and supporting classes, which use an RDBMS database (assumed to by MySQL) as an annotation store, and the file system as a file store.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnotationAgqlToSql
    Converts AGQL expressions into SQL queries for matching graphs (transcripts).
    AnnotationAgqlToSql.Query
    Encapsulates the results of AnnotationAgqlToSql.sqlFor(String,String,String,String) including the SQL.
    FragmentSeries
    An implementation of Spliterator<Graph> that enumerates fragments corresponding to a list of selected fragment Ids.
    GraphAgqlToSql
    Converts AGQL expressions into SQL queries for matching graphs (transcripts).
    GraphAgqlToSql.Query
    Encapsulates the results of GraphAgqlToSql.sqlFor(String,String,String,String,String) including the SQL.
    ParticipantAgqlToSql
    Converts AGQL expressions into SQL queries for matching participants.
    ParticipantAgqlToSql.Query
    Encapsulates the results of ParticipantAgqlToSql.sqlFor(String,String,String,String) including the SQL.
    ResultSeries
    An implementation of Spliterator<Graph> that enumerates fragments corresponding to a search result set.
    SqlConstants
    Constants relating to SQL annotation stores.
    SqlGraphStore
    Graph store that uses a relational database as its back end.
    SqlGraphStoreAdministration
    Graph store administration that uses a relational database as its back end.
